```class Solution {
    public int makeTheIntegerZero(int num1, int num2) {
        int res = 0;
        while (num1 != 0) {
            int i = Math.min(num1, 30);
            num1 -= 2 * i + num2;
            res += i;
            if (num1 < 0) {
                return -1;
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
